%h4 Meta data defaults
.row
  .col-md-4
    %p Meta data is automatically generated for pages in the CMS from the information on each page.

    %p Other pages, such as /login, will get the default meta information listed on the right.

    %p You can override this for other urls using this page

    %p Listed below are any existing meta data overrides.

  .col-md-8
    %dl
      %dt title
      %dd=Settings.default_meta_title
    %dl
      %dt description
      %dd=Settings.default_meta_description
    %dl
      %dt keywords
      %dd=Settings.default_meta_keywords
    %dl
      %dt image
      %dd=image_tag(Settings.default_fb_meta_image, class: 'pull-left')

%hr
